
- Requirements:

  - CMake.

  - A C++ compiler with C++14 support.
    The following compilers have been tested:
    - GCC 5.4 (Linux+GNU x86_64).
    - GCC 7.1 (Linux+GNU x86_64).
    - Clang 4.0 (Linux+GNU x86_64).

- Build:

  - Linux - GCC:
    - Execute in a terminal (running bash):

      pkg_dir=$PWD
      mkdir ../gama_tts-build
      cd ../gama_tts-build
      cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release $pkg_dir
      make

  - Linux - LLVM/Clang:
    - Execute in a terminal (running bash):

      pkg_dir=$PWD
      mkdir ../gama_tts-build
      cd ../gama_tts-build
      CXX=clang++ cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release $pkg_dir
      make

- Test (Linux):

  echo "Hello world." | ./gama_tts tts $pkg_dir/data/english/vtm5 test.wav

  # The "play" program is included in the SoX package.
  play test.wav

- Install to system (optional, Linux):

  make install

  # /usr/local/lib or /usr/local/lib64 must be in /etc/ld.so.conf
  # (or /etc/ld.so.conf.d).
  ldconfig
